1
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:18,500
Mother saw me and you sleeping together.

2
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:20,500
If we go back, I don't know what you will get.

3
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:21,500
My mother killed a man.

4
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:23,500
She needs to hide the secret that I'm a homosexual.

5
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,500
Tian disappeared along with Jiu.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,500
Do you want me to believe that Jiu did these alone?

7
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,500
Don't tell me that Chan is involved in this.

8
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:32,500
I definitely won't let her get away.

9
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:34,500
Mom!

10
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,500
Yang, it's not what you think.

11
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,500
No need to explain now. Run first.

12
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:39,500
Why?

13
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,500
Father is here.

14
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:41,500
Huh?

15
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:42,500
You sent him to hurt my son.

16
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:44,500
But this time, I can't stand it.

17
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:45,500
because you hurt my child.

18
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:47,500
Where is my son now?

19
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:50,500
I told you already that I didn't know where Tian is.

20
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,500
If anything happens to Tian, I'll kill you.

21
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:54,500
Yang.

22
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:57,500
Don't say anything. We have a lot to discuss at home.

23
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:01,500
What happened? Why are you tied like this?

24
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,500
Help me and my sister please.

25
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:06,500
Please take Mei with you. Don't worry about me.

26
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:07,500
Hurry!

27
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,500
Help me, help.

28
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,500
A culprit caught a child and went over there.

29
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,500
She is not feeling well at all.

30
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:05,500
I think we need to take her to the doctor urgently.

31
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,500
Okay.

32
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,500
And who is this girl?

33
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:16,500
I don't know either. I saw her being held captive so I helped her out.

34
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,500
But there was still a boy locked up there.

35
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:26,500
If he knows that you helped this child out, you'll get into trouble.

36
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:30,500
I think so too.

37
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,500
After the treatment,

38
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,500
we need to find a place to hide for this kid.

39
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:39,500
But what should we do?

40
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,500
Let her stay with me.

41
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,500
I will take care of her.

42
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:50,500
Thanks.

43
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:56,500
I must find out who this girl is.

44
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:11,500
Tell me who helped you.

45
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,500
I won't.

46
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,500
Are you going to tell me or not?

47
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,500
He's gonna die.

48
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:28,500
He just fainted.

49
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,500
Damn it.

50
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:31,500
So we don't know who helped them.

51
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:36,500
Or is it Madam Chan and her son?

52
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,500
When I sent them off, I let them go through the back exit.

53
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,500
They might see or hear a child cry.

54
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:44,500
Chan isn't a kind woman who helps abused children.

55
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,500
What if it's her son?

56
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:52,500
His mom is on our side.

57
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,500
Why would he want to have a problem with us?

58
00:04:56,500 --> 00:05:00,500
I am afraid that what happened today

59
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,500
might be Big Brother who did it

60
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,500
since he came here all of a sudden.

61
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:08,500
If Mr. Song really gets Mei,

62
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:10,500
we don't know what she will tell him.

63
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:14,500
And if they know our move, what should we do?

64
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,500
Jiu too.

65
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:21,500
If he knows his sister was gone, he won't accept this.

66
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,500
What are you doing?

67
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:40,500
I'm cleaning the floor.

68
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:46,500
You don't have to do. Let me do it.

69
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,500
Hey.

70
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:54,500
You think I can't do these things.

71
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,500
Even if someone has done this for me,

72
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,500
but I can do everything.

73
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,500
Sweeping the floor, mopping, doing the laundry, I can do it all.

74
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:08,500
Perhaps I can do it very well.

75
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,500
What are you laughing at?

76
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,500
You don't believe what I say?

77
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,500
I believe you.

78
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:26,500
But I don't think you're good enough.

79
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:30,500
Look, you're all dirty.

80
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,500
Let's eat.

81
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:50,500
I think we should buy some dried food.

82
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:54,500
I don't want you to leave home often.

83
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,500
I'm afraid people from my house will see you.

84
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:00,500
Sure.

85
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:04,500
Let me wash my hands first.

86
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,500
I think …

87
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:53,500
It's not that small here.

88
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:57,500
We should pick up Mei and Fu to stay here.

89
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,500
Those two wouldn't be uncomfortable.

90
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,500
I think they will like it here too.

91
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:16,500
Tian, if you don't want to go home now,

92
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,500
we can stay here for the time being.

93
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,500
I'll sell candy sugar sculpture again,

94
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,500
or find something for sale.

95
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:30,500
Once we get some money, we can move to another place.

96
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:33,500
Go to somewhere no one knows us.

97
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:36,500
Thank you

98
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,500
for letting me be part of your life.

99
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:43,500
I'm glad to meet you.

100
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,500
To like you.

101
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:51,500
I never thought that, in my life,

102
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:55,500
I will meet a good man like you.

103
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:06,500
I may not be as good as you think, Tian.

104
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:14,500
If one day I do something bad to you,

105
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,500
can you forgive me?

106
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:26,500
You say this, what do you mean?

107
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:37,500
I'll bring you some water.

108
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:20,500
You went to Mr. Ma's today. How was it?

109
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,500
He seemed scared.

110
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,500
I think he really didn't know

111
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:32,500
where Tian is.

112
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:35,500
Why do you think like that?

113
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:37,500
A man like Ma,

114
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,500
if he hold the winning hand,

115
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,500
he wouldn't let us do this.

116
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,500
He must have used Tian to threaten us.

117
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,500
How is Mr. Tian doing now?

118
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:54,500
Your subordinate sent out to look for him had no clue at all?

119
00:10:58,500 --> 00:11:01,500
How will Madam Li be like?

120
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,500
Tian has disappeared like this, she must be unsettled.

121
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,500
About this matter,

122
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,500
the more I think, the more I find it strange.

123
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:14,500
If Tian's disappearance was done by Jiu,

124
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:16,500
Why did Li …

125
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,500
let all the workers go to work outside the house?

126
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:24,500
It's like she allow this to happen.

127
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,500
I won't be surprised if it was Chan.

128
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:34,500
Because last time, she seemed to team up with Ma,

129
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,500
letting him to blame Li at Dong's funeral.

130
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:43,500
Everything seems complicated.

131
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:46,500
So how are you going to handle this?

132
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:48,500
I need to know

133
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,500
what this is about.

134
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,500
And who did this?

135
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:04,500
Get inside.

136
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:14,500
What are you thinking of doing?

137
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,500
Why did you bring me to your room?

138
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:17,500
Do you want to talk in the hall?

139
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,500
Aren't you afraid others will hear this?

140
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:24,500
You're misunderstanding me.

141
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:25,500
I just went shopping today.

142
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:29,500
It was near Mr. Ma's house, so I just dropped by to greet him.

143
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,500
Don't you make excuses.

144
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:32,500
Do you know what you've done?

145
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,500
If I didn't warn you today, do you know what will happen?

146
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,500
Don't go there again.

147
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,500
And tell me the truth.

148
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,500
What did you and Mr. Ma do together in the past?

149
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:50,500
About Jiu,

150
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:53,500
did you know that from the beginning?

151
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:57,500
And where did he take Tian to?

152
00:12:57,700 --> 00:13:00,500
Hey, I don't know. I don't know anything.

153
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:01,500
You're lying.

154
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:04,500
If you still don't tell me the truth,

155
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:06,500
I'm going to tell Father right now.

156
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,500
Wait, Yang.

157
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:10,500
You can't tell Father, otherwise I will surely die.

158
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,500
So tell me everything.

159
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,500
I just know that

160
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:24,500
Mr. Ma would send someone here,

161
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:26,500
but I really don't know who it is.

162
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:29,500
I just found out later

163
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,500
that it was Jiu.

164
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:36,500
So how am I supposed to know

165
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,500
where he took Tian to?

166
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:43,500
I'm telling the truth.

167
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,500
Jiu is Mr. Ma's subordinate.

168
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:03,500
So all this time,

169
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:08,500
Since he met Tian first time, saving his life, asking for job,

170
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:11,500
these are made to deceive Tian.

171
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:13,500
Tian shouldn't trust a guy like him.

172
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:16,500
I don't know where he takes Mr. Tian to?

173
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:19,500
And he already knows his secret.

174
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,500
If he tells Mr. Ma,

175
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:26,500
the position of the family leader and the association head must be revoked.

176
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,500
What should we do?

177
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,500
First of all, we need to find Tian quickly.

178
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:37,500
Then blame Ma and Chan to all the troubles.

179
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,500
And finally,

180
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:44,500
We have to Kill Jiu to let Tian's secret die with him.

181
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:49,500
These beetles have already gained power from orchid dust, Madam.

182
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:57,500
Soon we will get beetle orchid to get rid of Jiu.

183
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,500
How is the girl, doctor?

184
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:33,500
We need to talk.

185
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:37,500
What? The girl is addicted to opium?

186
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:42,500
Yes, the doctor said so. Her condition is severe.

187
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,500
How is it possible? She's still young.

188
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,500
It must be Mr. Ma.

189
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:53,500
This means this child must have something that Mr. Ma wants.

190
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:57,500
If she is treated, we’ll probably know about it.

191
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:02,500
So have you found Tian?

192
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,500
My father sent people to look for him, but still can't him yet.

193
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:10,500
And now I don't know where Jiu did him.

194
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:13,500
The workers searched at Jiu's old house and didn't find them.

195
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,500
The longer it passes, the more dangerous it becomes.

196
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,500
Auntie, two packs of noodles.

197
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,500
Okay.

198
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,500
Have you seen these two men in this picture?

199
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:05,500
No?

200
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:12,500
Excuse me, have you seen these two men?

201
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:15,500
No, I'm not familiar with them.

202
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:22,500
Hey, have you seen these two?

203
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,500
No.

204
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:24,500
No?

205
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:27,500
Right, not at all.

206
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:32,500
Hurry up, I'm in a hurry.

207
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,500
Are you done yet?

208
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:43,500
Here you are.

209
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:49,500
Excuse me, have you seen these two?

210
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:50,500
Oh, he's over there.

211
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:52,500
Jiu! Freeze!

212
00:18:57,500 --> 00:18:59,500
Where did you hide Tian?

213
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:02,500
Tell Mr. Song that Mr. Tian is fine.

214
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:03,500
Zhao, get him.

215
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:21,500
Don't come in, or I'll kill Bao.

216
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:37,500
Jiu.

217
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:40,500
What happened to you?

218
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:42,500
Who did this?

219
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:46,500
Your father.

220
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,500
Your father let people come after me.

221
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:54,500
Now they've been looking for us around.

222
00:20:06,500 --> 00:20:07,500
It hurts a bit.

223
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:23,500
My father sent people out looking for us like this,

224
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:24,500
we are in trouble.

225
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:33,500
I think I'd better go home.

226
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:36,500
Tian.

227
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:49,500
Is it hard to be with me?

228
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:55,500
I'm sorry that I can't take good care of you.

229
00:20:57,500 --> 00:21:02,500
But I understand that you've never had a hard time like this before.

230
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,500
You're so tired, aren't you?

231
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,500
But can you not leave me?

232
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:11,500
I promise I'll try to take better care of you.

233
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:13,500
I'll do better, Tian.

234
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:16,500
Don't leave me.

235
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,500
It's not like that at all.

236
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:23,500
I want to go home…

237
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:29,500
because I'm worried about you.

238
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:32,500
I am afraid that you will be in danger.

239
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:37,500
Today my father sent someone to hurt you.

240
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:40,500
I'm afraid that, in the future,

241
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,500
he might send someone to kill you instead.

242
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,500
Don't be afraid about that.

243
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:55,500
I can take care of myself.

244
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:18,500
You've found Jiu? What about Tian?

245
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,300
No.

246
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:22,500
But he let me tell you that Mr. Tian is okay.

247
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:26,500
I ask at the noodle shop, she said

248
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:27,500
he bought two packs.

249
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:31,500
Then Tian is probably still safe.

250
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:35,500
And Jiu bought food for him.

251
00:22:38,500 --> 00:22:39,500
What is he doing?

252
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,500
Kidnapping Tian, but didn't bring him to Ma.

253
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,500
Why is he keeping Tian to himself?

254
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:50,500
He might be planning, Sir.

255
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,500
So he keeps Tian for negotiation.

256
00:22:58,500 --> 00:22:59,500
Did they find Jiu?

257
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,500
If he took Tian,

258
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:03,500
why didn't he bring him to Mr. Ma?

259
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:06,500
Madam Li suspects that he may keep Mr. Tian for negotiation.

260
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:09,500
I think he wants money.

261
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:13,500
If he wants money,

262
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:18,500
then why didn't he contact Mr. Song to demand money?

263
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:23,500
Or why didn't he go to Mr. Ma to ask for more money?

264
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:27,500
Why did they run away and hide like this?

265
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,500
Right.

266
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,500
What is this?

267
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:37,500
If they are woman and man, I think that they have eloped.

268
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:40,500
You spoke nonsense.

269
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:45,500
Now, keep an eye on Madam Li.

270
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:47,500
If she makes a move, tell me immediately.

271
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,500
Yes, Madam.

272
