392
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,500
Like…

393
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:32,500
Zhang! Zhang! Zhang!

394
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:46,500
Please, Doctor.

395
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:49,500
Don't go back to the house again.

396
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:54,500
I promise that if this is over, I will be ordained to pay for karma.

397
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:58,500
