427
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:41,500
I'm sorry.

428
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:57,500
Doctor.

429
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:03,500
It's not true. Not true.

430
00:43:04,500 --> 00:43:05,500
I can't.

431
00:43:06,500 --> 00:43:08,500
Jia, Jia.

432
00:43:13,500 --> 00:43:16,500
