509
00:52:32,500 --> 00:52:33,500
Don't worry anymore.

510
00:52:36,500 --> 00:52:37,500
Dad.

511
00:52:38,500 --> 00:52:39,500
Mom.

512
00:52:40,500 --> 00:52:41,500
