531
00:54:55,500 --> 00:54:58,500
No one disgusts us, or sees us as abnormal.

532
00:54:59,500 --> 00:55:01,500
No homosexual thing.

533
00:55:02,500 --> 00:55:03,500
Only love.

534
00:55:05,500 --> 00:55:06,500
When that day comes,

535
00:55:07,500 --> 00:55:09,500
