536
00:55:15,500 --> 00:55:16,500
So you wait for me here.

537
00:55:17,500 --> 00:55:18,500
I'll go buy some food and I'll be right back.

538
00:55:23,500 --> 00:55:24,500
Hurry up.

539
00:55:39,500 --> 00:55:42,500
The doctor just checked the girl again this morning.

540
00:55:43,000 --> 00:55:45,500
