542
00:55:50,500 --> 00:55:51,500
Pin.

543
00:55:52,500 --> 00:55:54,500
Thanks. Please take care of it for me.

544
00:55:56,500 --> 00:55:59,500
I'm willing to help this girl.

545
00:56:00,500 --> 00:56:03,500
My father and Nangnoi also help me at home.

546
00:56:09,500 --> 00:56:10,500
Jiu.

547
00:56:11,500 --> 00:56:12,500
Yang.

548
00:56:13,500 --> 00:56:14,500
Yang. I'm sorry.

549
00:56:15,500 --> 00:56:18,500
Yang, Yang.

550
00:56:28,500 --> 00:56:30,500
Where do you hide Tian?

551
00:56:31,500 --> 00:56:33,500
Yang, listen to me first.

552
00:56:33,700 --> 00:56:34,500
Jiu.

553
00:56:34,800 --> 00:56:35,500
Please calm down.

554
00:56:39,500 --> 00:56:41,500
I know you're Mr. Ma's subordinate.

555
00:56:42,500 --> 00:56:43,500
Yang, listen to me.

556
00:56:49,500 --> 00:56:50,500
Jiu.

557
00:56:51,500 --> 00:56:53,500
I will never hurt Tian. I love him.

558
00:56:53,700 --> 00:56:56,500
Liar. You deceive him, right?

559
00:56:57,500 --> 00:56:58,500
You're going to tell Ma about him.

560
00:57:29,500 --> 00:57:30,500
Jiu.

561
00:57:39,500 --> 00:57:40,500
Yang

562
00:57:41,500 --> 00:57:42,500
Here.

563
00:57:47,500 --> 00:57:48,500
Pin.

564
00:57:49,500 --> 00:57:50,500
Tian.

565
00:57:51,500 --> 00:57:52,500
Tian.

566
00:57:53,500 --> 00:57:55,500
Where have you been?

567
00:57:56,500 --> 00:57:58,500
Everyone at home is very worried about you.

568
00:58:00,500 --> 00:58:02,500
So did Jiu hurt you?

569
00:58:02,800 --> 00:58:05,500
No, he didn't do anything.

570
00:58:07,500 --> 00:58:08,500
Do you have a pencil or a pen with you now?

571
00:58:10,500 --> 00:58:11,500
Yes.

572
00:58:15,500 --> 00:58:16,500
Here.

573
00:58:16,800 --> 00:58:19,500
Give Yang this letter and let him take it to Bua.

574
00:58:20,500 --> 00:58:22,500
Why do you have to leave a letter?

575
00:58:22,800 --> 00:58:23,500
Why didn't you go home?

576
00:58:24,500 --> 00:58:25,500
I can't go back now.

577
00:58:26,500 --> 00:58:27,500
I'll tell you later. It's a long story.

578
00:58:35,500 --> 00:58:36,500
But don't worry about me.

579
00:58:37,500 --> 00:58:38,500
Jiu is a good man. He won't harm me.

580
00:58:39,500 --> 00:58:40,500
Tian.

581
00:58:40,800 --> 00:58:42,500
Jiu is deceiving you.

582
00:58:43,500 --> 00:58:44,500
Jiu is a subordinate of …

583
00:58:44,700 --> 00:58:45,500
Tian.

584
00:58:47,500 --> 00:58:48,500
Tian, Jiu is…

585
00:58:48,500 --> 00:58:49,500
Tian, your brother is following me. Let's go.
Tian, Jiu is…

586
00:58:49,500 --> 00:58:50,500
Tian, your brother is following me. Let's go.

587
00:58:51,500 --> 00:58:52,500
Pin, please give it to Yang.

588
00:58:52,700 --> 00:58:52,900
Let's go.

589
00:58:52,900 --> 00:58:53,500
Tian, listen to me first.
Let's go.

590
00:58:53,500 --> 00:58:54,500
Tian, listen to me first.

591
00:58:54,700 --> 00:58:55,500
Tian.

592
00:58:56,500 --> 00:58:57,500
Tian.

593
00:58:57,800 --> 00:58:58,400
Tian.

594
00:58:58,500 --> 00:58:59,500
Yang.

595
00:59:05,500 --> 00:59:06,500
Yang.

596
00:59:06,700 --> 00:59:07,500
Sorry, Madam. / Tian!

597
00:59:08,500 --> 00:59:09,500
Pin.

598
00:59:10,500 --> 00:59:12,500
Don't get up yet.

599
00:59:23,500 --> 00:59:24,500
Where is Jew taking Tian to?

600
00:59:27,500 --> 00:59:28,500
Yang.

601
00:59:29,500 --> 00:59:30,500
Tian gave me a letter.

602
00:59:37,500 --> 00:59:38,500
Bua,

603
00:59:39,500 --> 00:59:41,500
please meet me at the shrine next to the market tomorrow night.

604
00:59:42,500 --> 00:59:43,500
Don't let anyone know.

605
00:59:47,500 --> 00:59:49,500
Jiu really captures Tian.

606
00:59:50,500 --> 00:59:52,500
That's why he has to send a letter asking for help.

607
00:59:57,500 --> 00:59:59,500
Perhaps it's not like that.

608
01:00:00,500 --> 01:00:02,500
Tian was talking to me for quite a long time.

609
01:00:03,500 --> 01:00:06,500
If he wanted to run away or go home, he could do it.

610
01:00:07,000 --> 01:00:09,500
But he chooses to go with Jiu.

611
01:00:12,500 --> 01:00:13,500
I think…

612
01:00:14,500 --> 01:00:16,500
Tian and Jiu,

613
01:00:17,500 --> 01:00:21,500
the two of them may have an unexpected relationship.

614
01:00:25,500 --> 01:00:26,500
You know about this?

615
01:00:28,500 --> 01:00:29,500
Yes.

616
01:00:30,500 --> 01:00:31,500
I can tell.

617
01:00:33,500 --> 01:00:35,500
I just realize now when you said

618
01:00:36,500 --> 01:00:37,500
Tian would never be able to love me.

619
01:00:39,500 --> 01:00:40,500
Pin.

620
01:00:41,500 --> 01:00:44,500
I beg you, don't tell this to anyone.

621
01:00:45,500 --> 01:00:47,500
I don't want Tian to suffer. Please, I beg of you.

622
01:00:48,000 --> 01:00:48,500
Okay.

623
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:55,500
All these years,

624
01:00:56,500 --> 01:00:58,500
Tian has lived a hard life.

625
01:00:59,500 --> 01:01:01,500
He has to hide what he is.

626
01:01:03,500 --> 01:01:07,500
I tried to ask him. I wanted to help and solve his problem,

627
01:01:10,500 --> 01:01:11,500
but he never told me.

628
01:01:16,500 --> 01:01:18,500
Until one day I learned the truth,

629
01:01:19,500 --> 01:01:21,500
I got it now

630
01:01:22,500 --> 01:01:24,500
why he can't tell anyone.

631
01:01:26,500 --> 01:01:32,500
You aren't angry or disgusted that he was like this, right?

632
01:01:33,500 --> 01:01:34,500
Not at all.

633
01:01:36,500 --> 01:01:37,500
No matter what he is,

634
01:01:39,500 --> 01:01:41,500
Tian is the brother that I love the most.

635
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:46,500
But it doesn't mean that people in this world will understand him like I do.

636
01:01:48,500 --> 01:01:51,500
There are still people who are taking advantage of this.

637
01:01:52,500 --> 01:01:53,500
If this secret is revealed,

638
01:01:54,200 --> 01:01:58,500
Mr. Ma will use this as an excuse to inherit the title of the Five Dragons Association's head.

639
01:01:59,100 --> 01:02:00,500
That's why he sent Jiu to deceive Tian.

640
01:02:04,500 --> 01:02:05,500
But…

641
01:02:06,500 --> 01:02:11,500
I think Jiu might not deceive Tian. He may really love him.

642
01:02:12,500 --> 01:02:14,500
That's not true. Not true.

643
01:02:15,500 --> 01:02:19,500
I don't believe it. There's no way he really loves my brother.

644
01:02:20,500 --> 01:02:21,500
He is the subordinate of Mr. Ma.

645
01:02:23,500 --> 01:02:26,500
I will find a way to help Tian no matter what.

646
01:02:52,500 --> 01:02:53,500
What bothers you?

647
01:02:57,500 --> 01:02:58,500
Many things.

648
01:03:01,500 --> 01:03:03,500
My father sent people to find us.

649
01:03:06,500 --> 01:03:08,500
You met Yang and got into a fight.

650
01:03:09,500 --> 01:03:11,500
Don't worry about that.

651
01:03:11,500 --> 01:03:13,500
I didn't hurt your brother.

652
01:03:13,500 --> 01:03:14,500
I know.

653
01:03:15,500 --> 01:03:17,500
Thank you anyway.

654
01:03:32,500 --> 01:03:33,500
Jiu.

655
01:03:35,500 --> 01:03:38,500
I don't think we can stay like this any longer.

656
01:03:38,500 --> 01:03:40,500
One day my father's people will find us.

657
01:03:41,500 --> 01:03:42,500
Tian.

658
01:03:43,500 --> 01:03:46,500
I will take better care of myself from now on.

659
01:03:46,500 --> 01:03:48,500
I won't go to a crowded place.

660
01:03:49,500 --> 01:03:50,500
Don't leave me, Tian.

661
01:03:51,500 --> 01:03:54,500
You know how important you are to me.

662
01:03:56,500 --> 01:04:00,500
In the past, I might live day by day without knowing my future.

663
01:04:01,500 --> 01:04:03,500
But after I found you,

664
01:04:04,500 --> 01:04:06,500
I want to be a better person

665
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:10,500
and do everything to make you and I very happy.

666
01:04:13,500 --> 01:04:15,500
Jiu, calm down.

667
01:04:17,500 --> 01:04:18,500
I'm not leaving you.

668
01:04:20,500 --> 01:04:22,500
I already got a plan.

669
01:04:24,500 --> 01:04:27,500
If I talk to Bua tomorrow,

670
01:04:29,500 --> 01:04:31,500
everything will probably end.

671
01:04:32,500 --> 01:04:33,500
Then we…

672
01:04:37,500 --> 01:04:38,500
we will be together.

673
01:04:40,500 --> 01:04:42,500
No one will look for us.

674
01:05:02,500 --> 01:05:06,500
Bua, please meet me at the shrine next to the market tomorrow night.

675
01:05:07,500 --> 01:05:08,500
Don't let anyone know.

676
01:05:10,500 --> 01:05:11,500
Mr. Tian's letter.

677
01:05:15,500 --> 01:05:16,500
So how are you going to do?

678
01:05:22,500 --> 01:05:23,500
Why are they talking here?

679
01:05:26,500 --> 01:05:27,500
And what's that paper?

680
01:05:29,500 --> 01:05:31,500
Bua and Yang discussed something?

681
01:05:31,900 --> 01:05:32,500
Yes, Madam.

682
01:05:33,500 --> 01:05:34,500
They looked suspicious.

683
01:05:35,000 --> 01:05:36,500
Should we call Bua to ask?

684
01:05:50,500 --> 01:05:51,500
Tian.

685
01:05:53,500 --> 01:05:54,500
You really won't let me go with you?

686
01:05:55,500 --> 01:05:57,500
I want to talk to Bua alone.

687
01:05:59,500 --> 01:06:00,500
One more thing,

688
01:06:01,000 --> 01:06:02,500
my father might send someone to follow me.

689
01:06:03,500 --> 01:06:06,500
And if they find you, they must hurt you for sure.

690
01:06:07,500 --> 01:06:08,500
But Tian...

691
01:06:08,700 --> 01:06:09,500
Don't worry.

692
01:06:13,500 --> 01:06:15,500
Today everything will end.

693
01:06:16,500 --> 01:06:19,500
I'll do anything for the two of us to be together.

694
01:06:20,500 --> 01:06:21,500
I promise you.

695
01:06:29,500 --> 01:06:30,500
Then let me walk you there.

696
01:06:32,500 --> 01:06:33,500
Let's go.

697
01:06:37,500 --> 01:06:39,500
Tell our people

698
01:06:40,500 --> 01:06:42,500
to destroy that bitch Xiaotong's teahouse.

699
01:06:43,500 --> 01:06:44,500
So she'll know that

700
01:06:45,500 --> 01:06:48,500
if she messes with my matter, what will she face?

701
01:06:49,200 --> 01:06:52,500
So she won't dare to tell Big Brother about me later.

702
01:06:53,500 --> 01:06:54,500
Yes, Sir.

703
01:06:59,500 --> 01:07:00,500
Sir.

704
01:07:06,500 --> 01:07:07,500
Jiu.

705
01:07:52,500 --> 01:07:56,500
We got the news about Jiu's hiding place, Sir.

706
01:07:56,900 --> 01:07:57,500
How is it?

707
01:07:58,000 --> 01:08:00,500
A fisherman found Mr. Tian and Jiu.

708
01:08:00,500 --> 01:08:03,500
He thought that their faces were familiar, just like in our notice.

709
01:08:03,500 --> 01:08:06,500
So he followed them. It turned out to be them.

710
01:08:06,500 --> 01:08:08,500
Now we know where the two of them are.

711
01:08:09,500 --> 01:08:11,500
Take me there right now.

712
01:08:35,500 --> 01:08:36,500
Tian, are you back?

713
01:08:44,500 --> 01:08:45,500
Mr. Ma.

714
01:09:11,500 --> 01:09:12,500
Bua,

715
01:09:14,500 --> 01:09:16,500
Yang didn't come with you?

716
01:09:18,500 --> 01:09:21,500
Bua, I can't stay long. I have to hurry.

717
01:09:22,500 --> 01:09:25,500
I want to say that I left the house

718
01:09:26,000 --> 01:09:28,500
not because someone caught or hurt me.

719
01:09:28,500 --> 01:09:30,500
I am willing to leave the house by myself.

720
01:09:30,500 --> 01:09:31,500
Bua,

721
01:09:33,500 --> 01:09:35,500
I don't want to go home anymore.

722
01:09:35,500 --> 01:09:39,500
I don't want to return to the position of the clan leader.

723
01:09:39,500 --> 01:09:41,500
I know I'm not worthy.

724
01:09:42,500 --> 01:09:44,500
I'm not like everyone else.

725
01:09:46,500 --> 01:09:50,500
I... I am someone that no one will accept.

726
01:09:52,500 --> 01:09:54,500
I love men, Bua.

727
01:09:55,500 --> 01:09:56,500
I love Jiu.

728
01:09:57,500 --> 01:10:00,500
We are going to live somewhere else. Please help me, Bua.

729
01:10:01,500 --> 01:10:03,500
Please go back and tell Father

730
01:10:03,500 --> 01:10:06,500
to stop looking for me. Just let us go.

731
01:10:09,500 --> 01:10:10,500
Please, Bua.

732
01:10:24,500 --> 01:10:26,500
So it's like this.

733
01:10:34,500 --> 01:10:35,500
Mother.

734
01:11:21,500 --> 01:11:24,500
Please let me go to be with the person I love.

735
01:11:24,900 --> 01:11:25,500
I beg you.

736
01:11:29,500 --> 01:11:30,500
The hut is over there, Sir.

737
01:11:34,500 --> 01:11:36,500
The relationship between these two is strange.

738
01:11:37,500 --> 01:11:38,500
You know about it, right?

739
01:11:39,000 --> 01:11:41,500
We have to finish this first before he shares Tian's secret.

740
01:11:42,500 --> 01:11:43,500
What shall we do?

741
01:11:45,500 --> 01:11:47,500
You couldn't tell me Tian's secret.

742
01:11:48,500 --> 01:11:50,500
I will kill him myself.
